Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Ui Hirasawa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hanging out with Azusa-chan for the first time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cute outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're going to that training camp with the Light Music Club, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am. It's three days and four nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister says that the one they all went last year turned out to be a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.76,0:00:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.78,0:00:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet she meant they practiced the whole time, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:00:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ui! Isn't this cute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:00:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.22,0:01:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, after all, the four of them play so amazingly well together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They must practice a lot there...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's my sister like when she's at the Light Music Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess she's kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She really doesn't practice at all and she gave me a pretty weird nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Azu-nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:02:58.59,Alternative,,0,0,0,,And she's all touchy-feely all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my sister really is warm and sweet, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, that wasn't exactly what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what is Yui-senpai doing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis doesn't handle heat very well. She hates air-conditioning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can picture her sprawled out on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.23,0:03:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been lying around the house all day lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's so cute when she's lying around. She's adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ui! Ui!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uiuiuiuiui...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:32.06,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do Ui and I see her sister so differently?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, lately I've been wishing I had a big sister who was a lot like Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think she's really nice, and cool, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Ritsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she's awfully irresponsible and completely unfocused. I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, who's unfocused?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Ritsu. Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:56.26,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm sorry. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I saw you two from outside and I decided to come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:58.94,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're by yourself today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio's out taking some summer classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you don't have to go to any, Ritsu-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Who, me? Summer classes? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me. I've been meaning to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mugi brings her own tea sets to the club room and fancy cakes and has vacation homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she come from a really rich family?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She even has a butler at home, and the family even leave the country some time to go on long vacations!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They really do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd sure be cool if they did, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you don't know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we give her a call and go hang out over at her place for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you sure? It's kind of short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird, she's not answering her cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll try her home number.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:04:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, somebody picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, is this Tsumugi's dad I'm speaking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I am in the employ of the Kotobuki family as their butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow! They really have a butler!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:09.18,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow! They really have a butler!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well uh... Would Tsumugi happen to be at home, right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, just calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry. But I'm afraid Miss Tsumugi is summering in Finland at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she is? Thank you very much then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have bothered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Told you? It's just exactly like I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to come over to my house? We have a nice watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Count me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You here, Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Watermelon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritsu and Azusa-chan decided to come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Ui...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's strangely soothing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just like she said.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:05:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be rough to be a teacher, and working during summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we have to go to seminars and whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys practicing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Light Music Club is gonna have a training camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And we were all wondering if you wanted to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A training camp, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She doesn't look too thrilled about it, does she?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I guess we'll just go by ourselves then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets mad when we DON'T ask her, and when we DO, this is her response!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad, she could've gone swimming and had a barbecue and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait for this training camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our first time together for a while, so why don't we go buy stuff for the training camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, by the way, what are we out here to buy today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Some brand-new gear for the band?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute swimsuits!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're ready to goof off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a feeling something like this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we're not gonna play around the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't trust you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we'll have to take some breaks, too. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I hadn't thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this loneliness I'm feeling?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's even more awesome than the last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the vacation home you said you couldn't borrow for us last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sorry. That home wasn't available for us this year, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I find this one rather cramped, but we just have to put up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have an even bigger one?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.49,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have an even bigger one?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, let's have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No playing until AFTER we practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanna have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Majority rules, then. I vote that we practice first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Play first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.59,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Play first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I vote for playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,An unexpected betrayal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:02.40,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I swear, they've got plenty of energy for goofing off. [ For the now, xxx practice ]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When Mugi says "playing," I wonder if she means...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that could never happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I didn't need this stuff, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to get rid of everything on the beach this instant! I don't want the yacht, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Back and forth, back and forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aren't we ever gonna get around to practicing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Azu-nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come out and play with us, Azu-nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You must be pretty bad at sports, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not! Bring it on! You'll see what I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Azusa has fit in with the club just fine, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Ritchan, you should look at this right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that all story about corn barnacles, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, a boy cut his foot on a corn barnacle, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Mio? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta move up some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what got into me--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A desert island?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Ritchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it. We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to the new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:26.62,Alternative,,0,0,0,,We've got to the new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Zipangu! The land of gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:29.81,Alternative,,0,0,0,,What the heck are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We all played out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all go eat and then call it a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What about band practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it. I knew we should've practiced instead of playing around out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But you played more than anybody, Azusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sunburned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, I'm gonna go practice, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All night long?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm beat... and I'm starving, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Suck it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awesome, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never used an amp like that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, let's hurry up and practice! These snares are brand new!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Talk about self-serving.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Azu-nyan, what's that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an electronic tuner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? What do you use a tuner for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You use it to tune your guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. You've never seen a tuner before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, this is the first one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you tune your guitar, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I do it by ear. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}S-She has perfect pitch!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no idea if she's amazing or not!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, and four!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that sounded really great, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You were great, Yui-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:14.56,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder when they had time to practice?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You set a perfect tempo over this long, too, Ritsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do some cram practicing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry that I've got absolutely no energy left...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the hunger made her lose her extra energy and play better than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's eat! Please feed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks, Ritsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritchan! We bring you meat! And veggies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A whole head of cabbage! I'm so hungry I'll eat it raw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Show a little patience, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They goof off all the time, but for some reason they manage to play really well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The god of cabbages is angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If we split up the cutting work, it'll be all ready in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:04.28,Alternative,,0,0,0,,The god of cabbages is angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll light the grill and start getting everything heated up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See, our new member is taking the initiative and working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes are burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui, sure you can handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When we die, we die together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready! So, why don't we make some onigiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're so different!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's just that you have man hands, Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was terrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That was awesome, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Who's for fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:14.48,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it burned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You know when fireworks is almost burned completely out, it sort of makes you wanna cheer it on, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it! You can do it! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It broke off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritchan, look! It's going out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! At times like this, we have to combine and get bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Combine! Form Sparklerman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, no fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that too heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's test our bravery!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not one thing, it's another...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to have a bravery contest. It's a camp tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm not doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you won't? You DO have a problem with scary stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can handle it just fine! So, bring it on, Ritsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, you're going to pay dearly for making me wait so long to eat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Seriously, Azusa, who still has bravery contests in high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, you're kinda hurting my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I bet it's Ritsu up to her usual tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio! Senpai! Pull it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yamanaka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Miss Yamanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? And what're you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my plan was to catch up with you and then surprise you all by my sudden arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you succeeded in surprising us, anyway. Regardless of how lost you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio-chan! Everything is all right! Mio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had no idea Mio got frightened so easily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That was total hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:06.85,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mio! Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Azusa, don't you like hot water?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Azu-nyan, at times like this, it's best to just get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because you were sunburned, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-chan, have you lost weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.76,0:17:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Didn't I tell you before? I can eat all I want, and I never gain any weight at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.08,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You, too, Miss Yamanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange but I really can't tell the two of you apart without my glasses on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll have to tell you apart based on bust size!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme the cabbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I didn't mean to make you practice with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it, Yui. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd been hoping that I might get a chance some time to practice with you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Azu-nyan, you're really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's my turn to give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this part is really tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should try playing it at a slower tempo at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Azu-nyan, I'm so glad I met you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Azu-nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Azu-nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Ui Hirasawa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hanging out with Azusa-chan again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Ui! Sorry, I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi! What kept you?\NWait, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I guess you didn't get in much practicing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We did practice some, but I was expecting more intensive training or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We basically goofed off most of the time swimming and stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wanted to practice a lot more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! That's weird. My sister wasn't tan at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get so sunburned?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I played around more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Still though...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really happy I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned lots of things about the others in the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? What kind of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, like Mio is more of a scaredy-cat than you'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she is? What about Ritsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, She IS unfocused and all, but she and Mio are great together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about Mugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, Mugi is sweet and generous and she's always thinking about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's got a childlike side to her that's fun and really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, what about my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Yui is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She buckled down and practiced!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.27,0:22:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She still stays glommed onto me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She's warm and sweet, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.20,0:23:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,These strings are all corroded.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When was the last time you changed them out for new ones, Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.30,0:23:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You mean you're supposed to change the strings?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.74,0:23:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.94,0:23:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a vintage guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.60,0:23:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we're sorry. It's just kinda dirty, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.42,0:24:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a year since I bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.68,0:24:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What if she decides not to come back to the club anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.12,0:24:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll happen to our concert at the school festival?
